com.simonecavazzoni.algraph.model

Class PriorityQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simonecavazzoni.algraph.model.PriorityQueue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of PriorityItem

    public class PriorityQueue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a PriorityQueue implemented with unordered ArrayList. This class exposes the methods to insert/delete/update/search PriorityItem.
